Sentence is withheld.   Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for five (5) years.   Conditions of probation are:
1) Write apology letters to all the organizations who will not benefit from the Van's Athletic Association as listed by Mr. Prickett.  Agent to approve letters.  
2) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
3) Maintain full-time employment and/or job search; 
4) Hold no job or position or volunteer where she is responsible for finances;
5) Assign her Federal and State tax returns over to Chief's Club;
6) Submit DNA sample and pay surcharge;
7) Pay costs of action; 
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
9) Spend four (4) months in jail, under the Huber Law, to commence on 02-11-16 by 5:00 p.m.  
10) Pay restitution of $15,500.00 to Chief's Club.   
Notice of Right to Seek Postconviction Relief.  
